description: One of the biggest Paranormal conventions in the country in Univ-Con at Penn State University, and it is run by Penn State Univerity's PRS!  Three of it's organizers and team members sit down with Darkness Radio to talk about this year's Conference and about a brand new show coming to TV that details their group called, Paranormal State!
